OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy and mild
OL,6,Fthroughout the day with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, this most persistent and
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy across Argyll.
OL,9,FChance of the odd brighter spell
OL,10,Fdeveloping towards Ayrshire later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be mostly cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of showery rain, heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes. Chance of a few clearer spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping towards morning. Windy at
OL,17,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
