OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FWindy as cloud and rain
OL,6,Fspread east through the morning, heavy
OL,7,Fat times. Clear spells and scattered,
OL,8,Fblustery showers through the evening.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,11,Fwith rain on Friday morning, becoming
OL,12,Fbrighter with a few showers later.
OL,13,FBright Saturday morning, before rain
OL,14,Fspreads east later. Cloudy and breezy
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
